00:26:17,400 --> 00:26:20,580
When you provide for
investigation on forensics,

536
00:26:20,580 --> 00:26:23,250
you provide and you can
perform full on incremental,

537
00:26:23,250 --> 00:26:26,370
but you provide the on
and we'll continue to scan

538
00:26:26,370 --> 00:26:29,850
providing you have the right
permissions given in the rule.

539
00:26:29,850 --> 00:26:33,030
And then on GuardDuty, you
